high_descs: Turn around and go to the dresser directly in front of you.
Take the soap bottle from the dresser.
Turn around, go toward the tub in front of you, then turn left and left again to reach the toilet.
Place the soap on the back of the toilet, to the left of the cylinder.
anns.task_desc: Put soap on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the stand with the soap dispenser on it, then turn right to face it.
Pick up the soap dispenser from the stand.
Turn around and walk to the bathtub then turn left and walk to the wall then turn left and face the toilet.
Put the soap dispenser on top of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Put a soap dispenser on top of the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn right and walk toward the closer bottle of soap.
Pick up the bottle of soap.
Turn around and walk to the toilet.
Put the bottle of soap on the top of the toilet, to the left of the empty toilet paper roll.
anns.task_desc: Put a bottle of soap on the top of the toilet.
